  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Different cities have different laws about such issues as carrying weapons in public and restricting spellcasters.\nThe city's laws may not affect all characters equally. A monk isn't hampered at all by a law about peace-bonding weapons, but a cleric is reduced to a fraction of his power if all holy symbols are confiscated at the city's gates.",
